r />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>黑 警 還 眼</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔只係口號咁簡單，我地要警察為佢地做過嘅事負責<br />\n<br />\n812咁成功，因為你同我都有參與<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地901一齊入機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記得係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1PM</span></span> 到機場吖<br />\n<br />\n誓要討回公道、要政府正面回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q：可能你會問，機場出咗禁制令，點解仲要入機場？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA：<br />\n禁制令=藐視法庭最多判幾月內(黃之峰坐左)<br />\n<br />\n非法集結起步判幾月<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪起步判3年以上至6年(梁天琦坐緊)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非法集會嚴重過藐視法庭啊</span></span><br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n明白個遊戲點玩未？？<br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜都咁多手足俾人拉咗，分分鐘坐幾年甚至十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你真係甘心佢地咁努力，然後我地白費曬佢地嘅心機？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有勇氣上街頭勇武<br />\n點解唔敢入機場？</span>"},{"pid":"5424a1fda373c9727f6cf08d1d4b506812617a46","tid":1512682,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"184701a4dd84df35d0779233c857fa75130688ec","tid":1512682,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得當初812我地點解要入機場<br />\n<br />\n依家係警察不停開槍射頭射眼，仲大條道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>黑 警 還 眼</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔只係口號咁簡單，我地要警察為佢地做過嘅事負責<br />\n<br />\n812咁成功，因為你同我都有參與<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地901一齊入機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記得係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1PM</span></span> 到機場吖<br />\n<br />\n誓要討回公道、要政府正面回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n________________________